-----BEGIN PGP SIGNED MESSAGE-----
Hash: SHA512

annotations:
  artifacthub.io/category: skip-prediction
  artifacthub.io/changes: |
    - kind: fixed
      description: PDB — maxUnavailable:0 and minAvailable:0 no longer trigger a false "not set" validation error; both values are now handled correctly in validation and rendering.
    - kind: fixed
      description: HPA — validation now fails if both targetCPUUtilizationPercentage and targetMemoryUtilizationPercentage are absent or zero, preventing an empty metrics list that Kubernetes rejects.
    - kind: changed
      description: release workflow — added timeout-minutes:30 so a hung chart-releaser or gh-pages push cannot occupy the runner for up to six hours.
    - kind: added
      description: persistence.mountPath — configurable uploads volume mount path; must match config.FILE_UPLOAD_DIR to prevent silent data loss on pod restart.
    - kind: fixed
      description: Validation now fails if config.FILE_UPLOAD_DIR and persistence.mountPath differ, catching a silent data-loss misconfiguration.
    - kind: fixed
      description: Validation now fails if config.FITPUB_PAGES_PATH and pages.mountPath differ, preventing Markdown pages from being invisibly missing at runtime.
    - kind: fixed
      description: productionChecks now validates FITPUB_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY when FITPUB_PUSH_ENABLED=true, preventing a broken push configuration from reaching production.
    - kind: fixed
      description: Validation now fails if serviceMonitor.scrapeTimeout is greater than or equal to serviceMonitor.interval, preventing Prometheus scrape errors.
    - kind: added
      description: diagnosticMode — run the container as sleep infinity for safe exec-based debugging without probe interference.
    - kind: added
      description: lifecycleHooks — configurable preStop/postStart hooks for graceful shutdown and load balancer drain.
    - kind: added
      description: priorityClassName, schedulerName, runtimeClassName — scheduling knobs for production cluster policies.
    - kind: added
      description: hostAliases, dnsPolicy, dnsConfig — DNS customization for federation testing and private resolvers.
    - kind: added
      description: commonLabels and commonAnnotations — apply labels and annotations to every chart resource from a single location.
    - kind: added
      description: command and args overrides for the main container entrypoint.
    - kind: added
      description: minReadySeconds for deployment stability window.
    - kind: fixed
      description: ServiceMonitor now includes namespaceSelector so Prometheus running in a different namespace can discover FitPub.
    - kind: fixed
      description: automountServiceAccountToken is now set on the pod spec in addition to the ServiceAccount, preventing token mount when an external SA is used.
    - kind: changed
      description: commonAnnotations propagated to all chart resources via a shared helper.
  artifacthub.io/containsSecurityUpdates: "false"
  artifacthub.io/images: |
    - name: fitpub
      image: codeberg.org/fitpub/fitpub:1.1.1
    - name: volume-permissions
      image: busybox:1.37
      whitelisted: true
  artifacthub.io/license: Apache-2.0
  artifacthub.io/prerelease: "false"
